rawQuery: q = [ from scan(public:adhoc10GB8W:lineitemHash) as d,scan(public:adhoc10GB:customerReplicate) as e,scan("public:adhoc10GB:partReplicate") as f where e.c_custkey = d.l_custkey and f.p_partkey = d.l_partkey emit c_nation,p_mfgr,p_type,c_nation_prefix,c_name,c_phone,l_orderpriority,p_container,c_region,c_address]; store(q, query384);
